title: 820-00165 No usb activity
message:
Clean board, no corrosion.

All test were done on bench nothing connected except for IO board and flex, I tested it without flex too and same problem.

Board has 1.8V PPVCC_S0_CPU 
CPU gets hot as if it is working, tries to boot but stays around 0.150A
PPVRTC_G3H 3.3V
PLT_RESET_L 3.3v 
U7100 27-28 and 17-18 measure normal

Already tried heating up CPU, clean BIOS on a new U6100, Working SMC but same problem.
